snippet.title: Hupsi - a musical adventure - trailer
snippet.description:
Hupsi is a playful and super adorable musical adventure for children. Everything is handcrafted and carefully designed for the 1-3 year-olds. 

The wonderful forest is full of friendly animals making music and sounds as you interact and explore. There is no wrong or right, just play, enjoy and learn.

The animals make up their own funny sounds so the music is without language and can be enjoyed by children of any age or language.The app contains NO ads or in-app purchases. 

We are 5 PM Kids, a tiny Scandinavian games studio, doing our best to bring beautiful high-quality children’s experiences to the mobile market. If you have any questions, don’t hesitate to ask us.
